---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about FutureScopeHub and our AI-powered approach to content.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <article class="article-content">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8">
          About <span class="text-[var(--color-neon-cyan)]">FutureScopeHub</span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)] to-[var(--color-deep-space)] border border-[var(--color-neon-cyan)]/30 mb-10">
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] m-0">
            We're not just another news site. We're an experiment in AI-augmented journalism, 
            where cutting-edge language models help curate and synthesize the stories that matter.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          In a world drowning in information, FutureScopeHub exists to be your intelligent filter. 
          We leverage advanced AI (powered by Google's Gemini 3) to scan hundreds of sources, 
          identify the signal in the noise, and deliver insights that are:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Timely</strong> ‚Äî Updated daily through automated pipelines</li>
          <li><strong>Verified</strong> ‚Äî Grounded with real-time search to prevent hallucinations</li>
          <li><strong>Engaging</strong> ‚Äî Written in a style that respects your time</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>
          Every day, our automated system:
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Scans RSS feeds and news APIs for trending stories in tech, entertainment, and world news</li>
          <li>Synthesizes multiple sources using Gemini 3 Flash for speed and Pro for refinement</li>
          <li>Verifies facts using Google Search Grounding to ensure accuracy</li>
          <li>Generates original imagery using Imagen 3</li>
          <li>Deploys to our lightning-fast static site via GitHub Actions</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2>The Human Element</h2>
        <p>
          While AI does the heavy lifting, every piece of content is reviewed before publication. 
          We believe in AI as a tool, not a replacement. The final editorial judgment‚Äîwhat to publish, 
          how to frame it, and when to add context‚Äîremains human.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Stack</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-8">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)]">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">‚ö°</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Astro</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Static Site Generator</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)]">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">ü§ñ</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Gemini 3</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">AI Intelligence</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)]">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">üöÄ</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">GitHub Actions</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Automation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-galaxy-dark)]">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">üåê</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">GitHub Pages</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Hosting (Free)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Got feedback? Found an error? We'd love to hear from you.
          <br />
          Reach out on Twitter/X: <a href="https://twitter.com/futurescopehub">@FutureScopeHub</a>
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
